<span class="t sl" style="left:50px;bottom:1002px;letter-spacing:0.17px;">WHAT IS ORIENTATION STYLE ? </span>
<span class="t sh" style="left:47px;bottom:954px;letter-spacing:-0.08px;">Orientation style identifies what an individual is driven by and how they interact with </span>
<span class="t sh" style="left:47px;bottom:923px;letter-spacing:-0.08px;">their surroundings. Understanding the orientation style will help you with career </span>
<span class="t sh" style="left:47px;bottom:892px;letter-spacing:-0.08px;">decision based on your dominant style. </span>
<span class="t sm" style="left:78px;bottom:1060px;letter-spacing:-0.07px;">ORIENTATION STYLE </span>
